data.description: Welcome to your dream country retreat! This charming 4 bedroom (includes 2 master suites), 3 bath house nestled on 10 acres of pristine land offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. The house itself exudes warmth and character, with its inviting design and touches throughout. The spacious living room includes a cozy fireplace. The  kitchen includes modern appliances, ample counter space, and a breakfast nook. The home includes a pole barn, separate guest house, dog pens, fenced in pasture with pond, horse stalls, tack room. Home has new AC units, roof, and reverse osmosis system.  Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a house on 10 acres of pure bliss. Whether you're seeking a weekend getaway or a permanent residence, this property will exceed your expectations.
